          "id": "b4d1295541e8cab0c5faac87366b5242b744f727",
          "message": "CI: prefer S3 aiter wheel before artifact fallback (#538)\n\n* CI: prefer S3 aiter wheel before artifact fallback\n\nTry the nightly S3 wheel index first so ATOM can pick up the newest amd-aiter build without waiting for artifact discovery. Fall back to the existing GitHub artifact lookup when the S3 index or wheel download is unavailable.\n\n* CI: resolve S3 wheel href before download\n\nUse the actual href from the nightly index so the workflow downloads the latest amd_aiter wheel from the correct location. Decode the wheel filename locally to preserve the expected package name and only fall back to artifacts when S3 is actually unavailable.\n\n* CI: use main wheel manifest before artifact fallback\n\nRead the latest main wheel manifest from S3 so ATOM downloads the explicit main branch wheel selected by aiter. Keep the existing GitHub artifact path as a fallback when the manifest fetch, validation, or wheel download fails.",
