          "id": "ef999d19340e1e109c2c0486b0a921847dde16a5",
          "message": "feat: add Qwen3.5 MTP support, dashboard MTP acceptance, model name normalization (#600)\n\nModel support:\n- Add Qwen3_5MTPModel with GDN hybrid attention (MTP1/MTP3)\n- Fix causal_conv1d_update VARLEN stride bug for GDN decode\n- Add MHA/MLA branching in EagleProposer for hybrid models\n- Add prepare_mtp_decode for GDN attention backend\n- Refactor MTP config to table-driven (_MTP_TYPE_MAP, _MTP_CONFIG)\n- Unify weight loading: weights_mapping + remap_mtp_weight_name\n- Fix scheduler preempt to strip MTP placeholder tokens\n\nDashboard:\n- Add MTP acceptance rate columns to accuracy table\n- Add model name normalization via models_map.js (HF path → display)\n- Fix modelFamily to handle space-separated quant/MTP suffixes\n- Add MTP acceptance mini chart with dual Y-axis\n- Add data point click popover for MTP acceptance chart\n- Fix accuracy filter to backend-only (show all models)\n- Fix parseBenchName for MTP acceptance/avg toks/fwd entries\n- Fix parseRunConfigs to skip entries without islOsl\n\nCI/Pipeline:\n- Replace inline benchmark transform with plugin_benchmark_to_dashboard.py\n- Inject benchmark_model_name from display field in workflow\n- Generate models_map.js from models.json HF paths at deploy time\n- Extract MTP acceptance from server log in accuracy tests\n- Add MTP acceptance entries in accuracy_to_dashboard.py\n- Add Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-FP8 MTP3 to nightly benchmark and accuracy\n\nDocs:\n- Update architecture, configuration, scheduling guides\n- Add Qwen3.5 recipe with MTP1/MTP3 commands\n- Rewrite add-model and debug-guide commands",
          "timestamp": "2026-04-18T21:09:33+08:00",
